{
  "stem": "1033.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's about 60, 80 kilometers from Budapest, where my grandparents owned a farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had, I think, 300 acres of vineyards and 200 acres of land of sorts, and raised, I think, four of their six daughters in this village.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother was born in 1900.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother, from stories I gather, was a very sensitive girl, and she didn't get along too well with her father, who was super religious.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother, I remember, read Oscar Wilde and other authors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in this time in Hungary, that wasn't the normal thing to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember her sisters mocking her, saying that she considered herself too good to live on the farm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And these sort of thoughts come to me much, much later on reflection.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At the time I, of course, didn't understand anything like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "All I knew was that I missed her affection very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she too, unfortunately, leaves a large gap in my own life in terms of having had a mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We went to-- to live with my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember crawling on the floor of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember, strangely, the underside of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember how-- how big people's feet were, and how when I looked up their behind was there, and way up there was up the person.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a person who seemed to have absorbed everything like a blotting paper.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even though I didn't know what to do with the information, it was there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spent a lot of time by myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandfather was the father figure in my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was super religious and a nervous man who had to think of money all the time, paying the people who worked the farm, and then having dowries.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
